WEBVTT

00:08:57.011 --> 00:09:00.552
But yet, the CEOs's pay
goes up and up and up.

00:09:00.979 --> 00:09:03.473
And so many people are left behind.

00:09:05.227 --> 00:09:07.178
I'm here to tell you:

00:09:07.202 --> 00:09:08.364
no more.

00:09:08.830 --> 00:09:11.552
It's not right, it's never been right.

00:09:12.648 --> 00:09:14.771
It's time to admit

00:09:14.795 --> 00:09:19.021
that the playbook that guided businesses
and CEOs for the last 40 years

00:09:19.045 --> 00:09:20.195
is broken.

00:09:20.625 --> 00:09:25.003
(Applause)

00:09:25.027 --> 00:09:27.963
It tells you everything about business

00:09:27.987 --> 00:09:31.104
except how to be a noble leader.